    <item>
      <title>由于电视前景恶化，派拉蒙债务被削减至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/paramount-debt-is-cut-to-junk-on-deteriorating-outlook-for-tv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级公司将派拉蒙全球公司的债务评级下调至垃圾级，该评级机构称，由于该公司的广播和有线电视业务持续下滑，现金流面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/paramount-debt-is-cut-to-junk-on-deteriorating-outlook-for-tv</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:43:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊向人工智能初创公司 Anthropic 投资 27.5 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/amazon-invests-additional-2-75-billion-in-ai-startup-anthropic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司表示，将向 Anthropic 追加投资 27.5 亿美元，完成去年达成的一项交易，以支持这家人工智能初创公司并扩大两家公司之间的合作伙伴关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/amazon-invests-additional-2-75-billion-in-ai-startup-anthropic</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:01:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Hedgeye 将其命名为一个简短的创意并暴跌 50%，Reddit 暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/reddit-tumbles-as-hedgeye-names-it-a-short-idea-sees-50-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Hedgeye Risk Management 发布报告称 Reddit 为空头，并表示其股价应下跌 50% 左右，Reddit Inc. 股价创下自该社交媒体公司上市以来的最大单日跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/reddit-tumbles-as-hedgeye-names-it-a-short-idea-sees-50-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:14:55 GMT</pubDate>
